\section{Projects}  

\textbf{Amazon Sales Analysis – Power BI Dashboard:} Built an interactive dashboard analyzing Amazon sales data from Excel. Used Time Intelligence DAX functions to calculate YTD, QTD, MTD, and YoY growth. Identified seasonal trends, moving averages, and peak performance periods. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/Amazon-Sales-Analysis}{GitHub})  


\textbf{End-to-End Real Estate Data Pipeline:} Developed a complete ETL pipeline to extract data from Redfin, store in AWS S3, process using Python, load into Snowflake via Snowpipe, and visualize in Power BI. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/StreamAnalysis}{GitHub})  

\textbf{Power BI Sales Dashboard:} Created dynamic Power BI reports for mobile sales trends (2021–2024). Integrated DAX for KPI tracking and trend analysis. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/DAX}{GitHub})  


\textbf{Sentiment Analysis Pipeline:} Built an automated pipeline for scraping Twitter data and analyzing sentiment using Python (Scikit-learn). Enhanced workflow automation and reduced manual analysis effort. (\href{https://github.com/Usama00004/Twitter-Sentiment-Analysis}{GitHub})  


